data.description: West Lancaster 8 Bed Home w/ a Spacious Backyard, Paved R.V. Access, And A 3 Car Garage, All Located On A Quiet Cul-De-Sac! NO HOA & NO Mello-Roos! High Ceilings Upon Entry w/ Plenty Of Natural Lighting And An Adjoining Formal Living & Formal Dining Area. The Spacious Kitchen Has Been Remodeled & Boasts Plenty Of Modern White Cabinetry, Stainless Steel Appliances, Quartz Counters, A Breakfast Nook, And Opens Up To The Family Room That Has A Cozy Fireplace! Five Spacious Bedrooms Upstairs. The Primary Master Suite Leads To A Private Balcony. Balcony Has Stairs That Lead To The Back Yard. Relax Or Entertain In Your Private Spacious Backyard That Has A Covered Patio. Side Yard Has Paved RV Access! This 8 Bedroom Home Is A MUST See! The Three Extra Bedrooms Are Currently Being Used For Senior Care. Each Spacious Room Fits Two Hospital Beds In Each Room. This Separate Part Of The Home Offers A Full Private Bathroom, Second Laundry Room And Office Space. Perfect Home For A Large Family or Two, a Senior Care Home, Transitional Home For Men, Women or Youth.
